  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1059">
<l>īvārka ṇeṉṉuṇṭān tōṟṟa mirantukōṇ</l>
<l>mēvāril lāta kaṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What (praise) would there be to givers (of alms) if there were no beggars to ask for and reveive (them).</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
